data.description: Located in a Cul-De-Sac Lot, Near Chandler Traditional-Goodman School, Upgrades feature a Gourmet Kitchen with Granite Countertops & Island, Including Stainless Steel Appliances & Refrigerator, Large Master Bedroom has Plush Neutral Carpet & Separate Entry. Bathroom Consist of His & Her Sinks with Tile Bath & Jacuzzi Tub with Jets, Large Walk in Closet, Large Formal Living Room & Dining Room that Flows into Light & Open Layout, Plantation Shutters, Ceiling Fans, Track Lighting, Oversized 24'' Travertine Stone in Kitchen & Bathrooms & Stone Surround Shower, Upstairs has a Bonus/Game Room with Adjacent Wet-Bar, While enjoying the Large Covered Patio Entertaining Area by the Pool, the Possibilities are Endless.
data.whatILove: Quite Cul-De- Sac, newly remodel, Large Master Bedroom with His and Hers Sink and Vanity, Large Covered Patio.
